凯莉·克拉克森说泰勒·斯威夫特在每次新专辑“重新发行”后都会送她礼物https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-says-taylor-swift-sends-her-gift-after-every-new-re-release-3536428?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kelly-克拉克森说泰勒·斯威夫特在每次新作品重新发布后都会给她送礼物Elizabeth AubreySat, 11 Nov 2023 14:09:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3536428 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·克拉克森和泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>凯莉·克拉克森透露泰勒·斯威夫特在她的专辑重新发行后给她送了一份礼物</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-says-taylor-swift-sends-her-gift-after-every-new-re-release-3536428">凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 表示泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在每次新的“重新发行”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上后都会送出她的礼物。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·克拉克森和泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kelly-Clarkson-and-Taylor-Swift-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-clarkson">凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson)</a>公开了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>最近重新发行《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-1989-taylors-version-breaks-two-spotify-records-3525033">1989</a> 》专辑后送给她的礼物。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">泰勒·斯威夫特 - “1989（泰勒版）”评论：她最好的专辑永远不会过时</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手于10月27日发行了她重新录制的《1989》，这是继《Fearless》、《Red》和《Speak Now》之后一系列重新录制的第四张专辑。</p><p>本周（11 月 9 日），克拉克森告诉<a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1389600/why-taylor-swift-sends-kelly-clarkson-flowers-after-every-re-recording" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="1"><em>E!</em></a>关于她在“泰勒版本”系列的每一次重新录制发行后如何收到斯威夫特的礼物的<a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1389600/why-taylor-swift-sends-kelly-clarkson-flowers-after-every-re-recording" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="1"><em>新闻</em></a>。早在 2019 年，克拉克森就向斯威夫特建议，在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swift-re-recordings-everything-we-know-3471197">与斯库特·布劳恩 (Scooter Braun) 就大师问题发生争执后，开始重新录制自己的音乐。</a></p><p>克拉克森当时在推特上写道：“@taylorswift13 只是一个想法，你应该重新录制所有你不拥有大师的歌曲，看看你到底是如何做到的，但要加入全新的艺术和某种激励措施，这样粉丝们就可以了。”不会再购买旧版本。我会购买所有新版本只是为了证明一点。”</p><p>从那时起，斯威夫特在每次重新录制发行后都会给克拉克森送花。<br /> “你知道什么这么好笑吗？她刚刚给我送了花，”克拉克森告诉媒体。 “她人很好。她做过。她就像是，‘每次我发布一些东西’——因为她刚刚发布了‘1989’。我还买了一件非常可爱的羊毛衫。” </p><blockquote 